			<node ID="ID_828189086" TEXT="Deployment diagrams are used to visualize the hardware processors/ nodes/ devices of a system the links of communication between them and the placement of software files on that hardware. In this UML deployment diagram tutorial we will cover what is a deployment diagram deployment diagram notations and how to draw one." />
			</node>
