		<node ID="ID_1989007960" LINK="https://www.lucidchart.com/pages/how-to-draw-a-timing-diagram-in-uml" TEXT="How to Draw a Timing Diagram in UML | Lucidchart">
			<node ID="ID_1798504751" TEXT="Step-by-step guide on how to draw a timing diagram in UML. Well show you how to create your very own timing diagram using UML best practices and include the variety of ways to publish and share your work. Use Lucidchart for all your UML diagramming needs when you sign up for a free Lucidchart account today!" />
